data.description: Gorgeous home in the desired community of Pecan Creek. Lots of space! 4 full bedrooms, plus a private office and a loft! Wood look tile throughout first floor, with laminate planks on second floor. No carpet in primary bedroom! Beautiful, matching quartz countertops in kitchen & bathrooms! Kitchen provides lots of cabinets, a central kitchen island & stainless-steel appliances. Primary is spacious and has ensuite bathroom with glass enclosed shower and large walk in closet. Home was just recently upgraded with gorgeous wood shutters and low maintenance turf/paved backyard. Ideal neighborhood location...right around the corner from elementary school, large greenbelt & playground. Come take a look!
